This socket head cap screw has a length of 45mm with a threading of M12 * 1.75mm [Fully Threaded]. It is made of Black-Oxide Alloy Steel, providing a mild resistance to corrosion in dry environments.

The cup point and the Grade 10.9 increases its strength against the pressure and has a tensile strength and hardness of 150,000 psi | Rockwell C32. Furthermore, it features a shear strenght of 90,000 psi.

ISO Metric Pitch | Coarse threads are an industry standard. These screws are classified as DIN 912 and comply with dimensional standards.
